32#include <core/client.h>

36#include <nvif/class.h>
37#include <nvif/unpack.h>
38
39int
40nv50_pior_power(NV50_DISP_MTHD_V1)
41{
42 struct nvkm_device *device = disp->base.engine.subdev.device;
43 const u32 soff = outp->or * 0x800;
44 union {
45 struct nv50_disp_pior_pwr_v0 v0;
46 } *args = data;
47 u32 ctrl, type;
48 int ret;
49
50 nvif_ioctl(object, "disp pior pwr size %d\n", size);
51 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
52 nvif_ioctl(object, "disp pior pwr vers %d state %d type %x\n",
53 args->v0.version, args->v0.state, args->v0.type);
54 if (args->v0.type > 0x0f)
55 return -EINVAL;
56 ctrl = !!args->v0.state;
57 type = args->v0.type;
58 } else
59 return ret;
60
61 nvkm_msec(device, 2000,
62 if (!(nvkm_rd32(device, 0x61e004 + soff) & 0x80000000))
63 break;
64 );
65 nvkm_mask(device, 0x61e004 + soff, 0x80000101, 0x80000000 | ctrl);
66 nvkm_msec(device, 2000,
67 if (!(nvkm_rd32(device, 0x61e004 + soff) & 0x80000000))
68 break;
69 );
70 disp->pior.type[outp->or] = type;
71 return 0;
72}

74/******************************************************************************
75 * TMDS
76 *****************************************************************************/
77static const struct nvkm_output_func
78nv50_pior_output_func = {
79};
80
81int
82nv50_pior_output_new(struct nvkm_disp *disp, int index,
83 struct dcb_output *dcbE, struct nvkm_output **poutp)
84{
85 return nvkm_output_new_(&nv50_pior_output_func, disp,
86 index, dcbE, poutp);
87}
88
89/******************************************************************************
90 * DisplayPort
91 *****************************************************************************/
92static int
93nv50_pior_output_dp_pattern(struct nvkm_output_dp *outp, int pattern)
94{
95 return 0;
96}
97
98static int
99nv50_pior_output_dp_lnk_pwr(struct nvkm_output_dp *outp, int nr)
100{
101 return 0;
102}
103
104static int
105nv50_pior_output_dp_lnk_ctl(struct nvkm_output_dp *outp,
106 int nr, int bw, bool ef)
107{
108 int ret = nvkm_i2c_aux_lnk_ctl(outp->aux, nr, bw, ef);
109 if (ret)
110 return ret;
111 return 1;
112}
113
114static const struct nvkm_output_dp_func
115nv50_pior_output_dp_func = {
116 .pattern = nv50_pior_output_dp_pattern,
117 .lnk_pwr = nv50_pior_output_dp_lnk_pwr,
118 .lnk_ctl = nv50_pior_output_dp_lnk_ctl,
119};
120
121int
122nv50_pior_dp_new(struct nvkm_disp *disp, int index, struct dcb_output *dcbE,
123 struct nvkm_output **poutp)
124{
125 struct nvkm_i2c *i2c = disp->engine.subdev.device->i2c;
126 struct nvkm_i2c_aux *aux =
127 nvkm_i2c_aux_find(i2c, NVKM_I2C_AUX_EXT(dcbE->extdev));
128 struct nvkm_output_dp *outp;
129
130 if (!(outp = kzalloc(sizeof(*outp), GFP_KERNEL)))
131 return -ENOMEM;
132 *poutp = &outp->base;
133
134 return nvkm_output_dp_ctor(&nv50_pior_output_dp_func, disp,
135 index, dcbE, aux, outp);
136}
